byline.original: Wireless to THE NEW YORK TIMES

abstract: Arrives in Brit with 2d Canadian Div
snippet: LONDON, Aug. 2--The arrival in Great Britain of the Second Division of the Canadian Active Service Force was announced today....

headline.main: 20,000 More Canadian Troops in England; Hundreds of Americans in Second Contingent

lead_paragraph: LONDON, Aug. 2--The arrival in Great Britain of the Second Division of the Canadian Active Service Force was announced today.
